worker

Class Worker

  • java.lang.Object
    • worker.Worker
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Runnable

    public class Worker
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Runnable
    Class in charge of the work flow of the worker flow: 1. Take an url to parse from the tasks to do queue 2. parse it with the OCRParser class 3. send result to manager and repeat stage 1-3 until termination
